{"tid":521274,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[朱經緯事件有感] 今時今日咁既社會，大家會點樣教自己仔女","createTime":"2018-01-06T11:24:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-06T15:41:41.000Z","uid":149494,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"dde7930c9110ddf382c2fdb9ac3bbaee2dc8820d","tid":521274,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T11:24:41.000Z","msg":"舉個例︰<br />\n子女見到朱經緯事件，明明從電視畫面上見到警察用棍打途人，法官又判左<br />\n但社會上有好多人覺得朱SIR根本無錯，連職責係保護巿民既警察都對法官判決不服，繼續撐朱SIR<br />\n投考警隊既中大BBA高材生又好有批判思考地話電視畫面信唔過<br />\n<br />\n你係父母,單單就呢單野,會點教子女"},{"pid":"fcd5492e0c73538f3ebb06d615be831d4aba16dc","tid":521274,"uid":15719,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T11:27:01.000Z","msg":"教佢揾多d錢"},{"pid":"bf1381560fed80300b1cf3fa54c5a66ddf06fc4b","tid":521274,"uid":41116,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T11:34:01.000Z","msg":"好仔唔當差<br />\n個個差佬都無好死（佢個年代）<br />\n老母不嬲都係咁教"},{"pid":"bd857056f7a2484fc66fa721f5703b66fbad0057","tid":521274,"uid":8632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T14:50:36.000Z","msg":"今時今日仲生仔？"},{"pid":"1e49df1a219a3b7f525714d8e745d01624d98f82","tid":521274,"uid":88029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T14:53:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4b57571b322fc90716a897d3122e5f3d376c5bb6","tid":521274,"uid":10453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T15:41:41.000Z","msg":"好好地讀書，讀唔成書就要做警察坐監<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}